-- Balfour Beatty rejects revised Carillion proposal
-- By Li-mei Hoang
-- Mon Aug 11, 2014 02:19AM EDT
-- None



LONDON, Aug 11 (Reuters) - British infrastructure company Balfour Beatty <BALF.L> said it has rejected a second proposal from rival Carillion <CLLN.L> to merge, citing the significant risks the deal would pose to its business.

